{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Me1Gw73xVbEEgxEmAVV2di","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have extracted all the required information from the coinflip.json file. Here's the comprehensive breakdown:\n\n---\n\n## **Account Requirements by Instruction**\n\n### **1. createMatch**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| creator | Yes | Yes | Player creating the match; funds escrow |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA (seeds: [b\"match\", creator]) |\n| config | No | No | Config PDA (read-only, for pause check) |\n| system_program | No | No | System program |\n\n---\n\n### **2. joinMatch**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| opponent | Yes | Yes | Opponent joining; funds escrow |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA to join (seeds: [b\"match\", coinflip_match.creator]) |\n| config | No | No | Config PDA |\n| orao_program | No | No | Orao VRF program |\n| orao_network_state | Yes | No | Orao network state PDA |\n| orao_treasury | Yes | No | Orao treasury for VRF fee payment |\n| orao_random | Yes | No | Orao randomness account (created by Orao CPI) |\n| system_program | No | No | System program |\n\n---\n\n### **3. cancelMatch**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| creator | Yes | Yes | Creator cancelling their match |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA (closed on cancel; escrow + rent refunded) |\n| system_program | No | No | System program |\n\n---\n\n### **4. timeoutCancel**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| caller | Yes | Yes | Any signer (permissionless after deadline) |\n| creator | Yes | No | Creator account; receives entry refund + rent |\n| opponent | Yes | No | Opponent account; receives entry refund |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA (closed after refunds; seeds: [b\"match\", coinflip_match.creator]) |\n| randomness_account | No | No | Orao randomness PDA (used to check VRF is NOT fulfilled) |\n\n---\n\n### **5. claimPayout**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| caller | Yes | Yes | Either creator or opponent can trigger claim |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA (closed after claim; seeds: [b\"match\", coinflip_match.creator]) |\n| config | No | No | Config PDA (for treasury address + CPI signing) |\n| treasury | Yes | No | Treasury account to receive fees |\n| creator | Yes | No | Creator account (receives rent refund on close) |\n| opponent | Yes | No | Opponent account |\n| randomness_account | No | No | Orao randomness PDA (must match vrf_request_key on match) |\n| creator_profile | Yes | No | Creator's player profile PDA on platform program |\n| opponent_profile | Yes | No | Opponent's player profile PDA on platform program |\n| platform_program | No | No | Platform program for CPI calls |\n| system_program | No | No | System program |\n\n---\n\n## **CoinflipMatch Account Fields**\n\nThe `CoinflipMatch` struct contains the following fields:\n\n| Field Name | Type | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| creator | pubkey | The player who created the match |\n| opponent | pubkey | The player who joined (Pubkey::default() if empty) |\n| tier | u8 | Tier index (0-5) |\n| entry_amount | u64 | Entry amount in lamports (derived from tier) |\n| creator_side | u8 | Side chosen by creator (0 = Heads, 1 = Tails) |\n| phase | RoundPhase | Current phase: Waiting, Active, Locked, Resolving, Settled, or Refunded |\n| result | u8 | Winning side after VRF resolution (0 or 1, only valid when settled) |\n| winner | pubkey | Winner's pubkey (Pubkey::default() until settled) |\n| claimed | bool | Whether the payout has been claimed |\n| created_at | i64 | Unix timestamp when match was created |\n| locked_at | i64 | Unix timestamp when match entered LOCKED phase (0 if still WAITING) |\n| resolve_deadline | i64 | Deadline for VRF resolution; after this, timeout refund is available |\n| vrf_request_key | pubkey | Address of the Orao randomness PDA for VRF lookup at claim time |\n| bump | u8 | Bump seed for PDA derivation |\n\n**PDA Seeds**: `[b\"match\", creator.key().as_ref()]`"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ae77103d67d569707 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 36314\ntool_uses: 1\nduration_ms: 12759</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d7619d26-977f-447b-8d13-946b8a80fc7d","uuid":"50de4fd3-4532-482c-84ca-0f0aec2842f7","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the file `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/coinflip.json` and extract the accounts required for each instruction: createMatch, joinMatch, cancelMatch, timeoutCancel, claimPayout. List all account names and whether they're writable/signer for each instruction. Also extract the CoinflipMatch account fields.","agentId":"ae77103d67d569707","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have extracted all the required information from the coinflip.json file. Here's the comprehensive breakdown:\n\n---\n\n## **Account Requirements by Instruction**\n\n### **1. createMatch**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| creator | Yes | Yes | Player creating the match; funds escrow |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA (seeds: [b\"match\", creator]) |\n| config | No | No | Config PDA (read-only, for pause check) |\n| system_program | No | No | System program |\n\n---\n\n### **2. joinMatch**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| opponent | Yes | Yes | Opponent joining; funds escrow |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA to join (seeds: [b\"match\", coinflip_match.creator]) |\n| config | No | No | Config PDA |\n| orao_program | No | No | Orao VRF program |\n| orao_network_state | Yes | No | Orao network state PDA |\n| orao_treasury | Yes | No | Orao treasury for VRF fee payment |\n| orao_random | Yes | No | Orao randomness account (created by Orao CPI) |\n| system_program | No | No | System program |\n\n---\n\n### **3. cancelMatch**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| creator | Yes | Yes | Creator cancelling their match |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA (closed on cancel; escrow + rent refunded) |\n| system_program | No | No | System program |\n\n---\n\n### **4. timeoutCancel**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| caller | Yes | Yes | Any signer (permissionless after deadline) |\n| creator | Yes | No | Creator account; receives entry refund + rent |\n| opponent | Yes | No | Opponent account; receives entry refund |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA (closed after refunds; seeds: [b\"match\", coinflip_match.creator]) |\n| randomness_account | No | No | Orao randomness PDA (used to check VRF is NOT fulfilled) |\n\n---\n\n### **5. claimPayout**\n| Account Name | Writable | Signer | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| caller | Yes | Yes | Either creator or opponent can trigger claim |\n| coinflip_match | Yes | No | Match PDA (closed after claim; seeds: [b\"match\", coinflip_match.creator]) |\n| config | No | No | Config PDA (for treasury address + CPI signing) |\n| treasury | Yes | No | Treasury account to receive fees |\n| creator | Yes | No | Creator account (receives rent refund on close) |\n| opponent | Yes | No | Opponent account |\n| randomness_account | No | No | Orao randomness PDA (must match vrf_request_key on match) |\n| creator_profile | Yes | No | Creator's player profile PDA on platform program |\n| opponent_profile | Yes | No | Opponent's player profile PDA on platform program |\n| platform_program | No | No | Platform program for CPI calls |\n| system_program | No | No | System program |\n\n---\n\n## **CoinflipMatch Account Fields**\n\nThe `CoinflipMatch` struct contains the following fields:\n\n| Field Name | Type | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| creator | pubkey | The player who created the match |\n| opponent | pubkey | The player who joined (Pubkey::default() if empty) |\n| tier | u8 | Tier index (0-5) |\n| entry_amount | u64 | Entry amount in lamports (derived from tier) |\n| creator_side | u8 | Side chosen by creator (0 = Heads, 1 = Tails) |\n| phase | RoundPhase | Current phase: Waiting, Active, Locked, Resolving, Settled, or Refunded |\n| result | u8 | Winning side after VRF resolution (0 or 1, only valid when settled) |\n| winner | pubkey | Winner's pubkey (Pubkey::default() until settled) |\n| claimed | bool | Whether the payout has been claimed |\n| created_at | i64 | Unix timestamp when match was created |\n| locked_at | i64 | Unix timestamp when match entered LOCKED phase (0 if still WAITING) |\n| resolve_deadline | i64 | Deadline for VRF resolution; after this, timeout refund is available |\n| vrf_request_key | pubkey | Address of the Orao randomness PDA for VRF lookup at claim time |\n| bump | u8 | Bump seed for PDA derivation |\n\n**PDA Seeds**: `[b\"match\", creator.key().as_ref()]`"}],"totalDurationMs":12759,"totalTokens":36314,"totalToolUseCount":1,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":10570,"cache_read_input_tokens":24524,"output_tokens":1215,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":10570,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
